Now, I want to live with dignity.

8
00:00:42,220 --> 00:00:43,340
Mr. Wang,

9
00:00:43,340 --> 00:00:45,020
since we've agreed to work together,

10
00:00:45,300 --> 00:00:46,180
I'll be frank.

11
00:00:47,566 --> 00:00:48,933
I've found out

12
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:50,600
that Liu Zhiqiang and Shangguan Chunyan

13
00:00:50,600 --> 00:00:52,233
framed my father,

14
00:00:54,233 --> 00:00:55,433
but there's someone else

15
00:00:55,433 --> 00:00:56,500
hiding behind the scenes,

16
00:00:56,940 --> 00:00:59,000
and I haven't been able
to uncover their identity.

17
