You should know more

18
00:01:03,740 --> 00:01:05,420
about this matter, right?

19
00:01:05,420 --> 00:01:06,533
I've kept it to myself

20
00:01:06,966 --> 00:01:08,500
for a long time.

21
00:01:09,300 --> 00:01:11,100
Before I tell you,

22
00:01:11,100 --> 00:01:12,733
you have to be prepared.

23
00:01:17,300 --> 00:01:20,600
The day after tomorrow
is the company's listing.

24
00:01:20,633 --> 00:01:21,766
Let's have

25
00:01:21,766 --> 00:01:23,780
a good celebration tonight.

26
00:01:26,220 --> 00:01:26,866
Cheers.

27
00:01:32,580 --> 00:01:33,700
Congratulations,

28
00:01:33,860 --> 00:01:35,460
my good friend.

29
00:01:36,660 --> 00:01:38,600
The Yun family and Shangguan family
are one.

30
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:40,300
Thank you, Yun Su.

31
00:01:40,300 --> 00:01:41,980
You two are awfully close.

32
00:01:42,300 --> 00:01:43,740
What about me?

33
00:01:45,580 --> 00:01:47,166
Look at you, Mr. Xiao.

34
00:01:47,460 --> 00:01:49,820
Here. I'll drink with you.

35
00:01:50,780 --> 00:01:51,800
No need.

36
00:01:52,700 --> 00:01:54,020
I want to thank my wife.

37
00:02:02,940 --> 00:02:03,740
What's wrong?

38
00:02:03,740 --> 00:02:04,820
Do you want to go back and rest first?

39
00:02:05,139 --> 00:02:06,432
With so many people,

40
00:02:07,333 --> 00:02:08,420
I can't leave.

41
00:02:11,420 --> 00:02:12,633
Shangguan Xiao,

42
00:02:12,966 --> 00:02:14,780
I didn't know
you were such a lightweight.

43
00:02:14,780 --> 00:02:16,380
Already swaying after a few drinks?

44
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,340
Come on. Get up.

45
00:02:18,660 --> 00:02:19,460
Let me.

46
00:02:20,060 --> 00:02:22,133
My husband needs
to pick up something in his room.

47
00:02:22,133 --> 00:02:22,140
He'll be right back.
